# Grouper 0.9

TODO Sync with Basecamp

## Next Actions
* Switch to _LinkedHashSet_
* Test with JDBC subject adapter
  * Have setup install subjects and teardown remove them?
  * Test with real subjects or add memory subject adapter
* Load group attributes into group subjects
* GrouperNamingPrivilege.getSubjectsWithPriv(s, ns, priv)
  * GrouperAccessPrivilege.getSubjectsWithPriv(s, g, priv)
* GrouperNamingPrivilege.revokePriv(s, g, priv)
  * GrouperAccessPrivilege.revokePriv(s, ns, priv)
* GrouperNamingPrivilege.getStemsWhereSubjectHasPriv(s, subj, priv)
  * GrouperAccessPrivilege.getGroupsWhereSubjectHasPriv(s, subj, priv)
* Return _AccessPrivilege_ and _NamingPrivilege_ objects
* ALL subject adapter
* Verify privileges within API
* Implement all 0.6 query filters
  * GroupAttributeMatchFilter
  * GroupAnyAttributeFilter

## Later
* Review exceptions
  * Should MemberNotFound and SubjectNotFound be replaced by Runtime
    exceptions?  Or at least be used more selectively?
  * should PrivilegeNotFoundException and SchemaException be merged?
    * Or just remove PNFE?
* _Stem_ child stems mapping
* _Stem_ parent stem mapping
* _Group_ parent stem mapping
* Commons logging
* More effective membership testing
* Custom list types
* Group deletion when groups have members or are members
* Switch to Hibernate 3.x
* Review generated SQL
* Test with Pg and Oracle and review generated SQL
* Review old _*.todo_ test classes
* Add create member and time to memberships
* Add create time to members
* Rename subjectIDs in local subject<=>member mapping (#133)
* Update and expend query api javadocs
* Review files and add TODO items to this list
* Review exceptions
* Map _GroupType_
* many-to-many maping between _Field_ and _GroupType_
* Replace `_init()` methods with static {} declarations where possible
* Replace contrib with updated cdg
* Test concurrent mods and access
* Custom group types
* Custom group attributes
* Custom group lists

